title: Pudhu Nellu Pudhu Nathu
subTitle: An old widow returns to her village with her two sons. The elder son is an illiterate peasant, the younger an educated, urbane youth, who falls in love with an iron-fisted local landlord's daughter.

title: Ulavuthurai
subTitle: Vasanth Periyasamy, a naval officer, is assigned to investigate the mysterious deaths at the sea. To protect his family, he assumes the identity of a car driver.

title: Thazhuvatha Kaigal
subTitle: Gopal and Rajeswari live a happy married life with their children. However, things start to change when he finds out that his wife suffers from blood cancer.

title: Ullathai Allitha
subTitle: Tired of his father's disciplinarian ways and to avoid marrying a girl chosen by the latter, Raja runs away to Ooty. There, he is hired as a driver by the man whose daughter he was supposed to marry.

title: Dhinamum Ennai Gavani
subTitle: Jai Kumar, a police officer, arrests Rolex, an international smuggler and puts him behind bars. Later, he escapes and the manhunt indicates revenge.

title: Thaaya Tharama
subTitle: A man and a woman fall in love. Later, he approaches her mother and asks for her hand, despite his parents' disapproval.

title: Thangamana Purushan
subTitle: Raja and Subalatha fall in love with each other. However, Raja's father, Aldapu Arumugam, and Subalatha's mother, Kanchanamala, are both extremely greedy and refuse to accept their relationship.

title: Thalaimagan
